    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DETAILED SURVEY OF INVENTORY COSTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Management wants to present the results of a detailed survey of inventory costs for different products, showing the current month, prior month, prior year, and percentage changes."</data>
      <data key="d2">a65f7c228e32e13ec5bad9f87503b9c1</data>
      <data key="d3">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d4">1</data>
      <data key="d5">98</data>
      <data key="d6">252cc8452bfc4c2aa58cab68d8b61879</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;EMPLOYEE TIME AND PRODUCT QUALITY LINK&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A factory supervisor wants to compare recorded employee time spent on producing each unit of a product and its final quality score to determine if there is any link."</data>
      <data key="d2">a65f7c228e32e13ec5bad9f87503b9c1</data>
      <data key="d3">"CONCEPTS"</data>
