    <node id="&quot;PROFIT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Profit" is the financial gain realized when the amount of revenue gained exceeds the expenses, costs, and taxes involved in sustaining the activity. It is obtained when the revenue from sales surpasses the total costs of production.</data>
