    <node id="&quot;BUDGETED SALES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Budgeted sales" are the estimated sales volume or revenue that a company expects to achieve in a future period. This projection represents the anticipated amount of sales revenue for a specified timeframe, providing a financial target for the company to aim for.</data>
