    <node id="&quot;SELLING PRICE PER UNIT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">The "SELLING PRICE PER UNIT" is the amount a customer pays for a single unit of a product or service. For products C, S, and D, the selling prices per unit are $110, $160, and $120 respectively. The selling price per unit remains constant, as indicated by the straight line of total revenue.</data>
