    <node id="&quot;GOAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">A goal is a desired result or outcome that a person or organization aims to achieve. It serves as a longer-term aspiration that guides an organization's objectives and performance measurement.</data>
