    <node id="&quot;MATERIAL&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Material" is the matter from which a thing is or can be made. It refers to the raw materials used in production. In this context, material is the only limiting factor in month 1.</data>
