    <node id="&quot;COST EQUATION QUIZ&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Cost Equation Quiz involves finding the linear equation y = a + bx, where y is cost, and x is output level, based on given data. It also requires forecasting the next month's cost if output is expected to be 4,500 units."</data>
      <data key="d2">ac59038d88c0dcce6b890bd17e7b2544</data>
