    <node id="&quot;LEVELS OF MANAGEMENT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Levels of Management refer to the different layers of management within an organization, typically including strategic, tactical, and operational levels."</data>
      <data key="d2">9cb3ca1f088473aac339bd044b8a7507</data>
      <data key="d4">1</data>
      <data key="d5">1223</data>
