    <node id="&quot;QUIZ: BUDGETED OVERHEAD COSTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves calculating the budgeted overhead cost per unit of the product 'Me' using activity-based costing. It provides information on production set-up costs, ordering costs, and other overhead costs, and requires the calculation of overhead costs per unit."</data>
      <data key="d2">77faaf4508d4f0bb2edf2e8e59bafd89</data>
      <data key="d7">0</data>
