    <node id="&quot;QUIZ: FIXED OVERHEAD COSTS IN ABC&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves calculating the budgeted fixed overhead cost per unit of product 'Ed' using activity-based costing. It provides information on material costs, labor costs, machine hours, and fixed overheads, and requires the calculation of fixed overhead costs per unit."</data>
      <data key="d2">77faaf4508d4f0bb2edf2e8e59bafd89</data>
