    <node id="&quot;QUIZ: ADVANTAGES OF ABC&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves identifying the advantages of using activity-based costing (ABC). It provides statements about ABC and requires selecting the correct advantages."</data>
