    </node>
    <node id="&quot;QUIZ: THROUGHPUT CONTRIBUTION RANKING&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves ranking products based on their throughput contribution to maximize production efficiency. It provides information on selling price, material cost, variable costs, and time taken in the dyeing process for three products."</data>
      <data key="d2">77faaf4508d4f0bb2edf2e8e59bafd89</data>
