    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FLEXED BUDGET STATEMENTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The quiz on flexed budgets involves identifying correct statements about flexed budgets, including their preparation at expected activity levels, use for identifying variances due to different activity levels, and reliance on original budget assumptions."</data>
      <data key="d2">ae2d4ea94e8ed5a50e75345ffd684969</data>
