    </node>
    <node id="&quot;STANDARD COSTING USE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The quiz on standard costing use involves identifying activities for which standard costing would not be used, such as determining expenses for reporting to shareholders."</data>
