    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MATERIALS VARIANCE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The quiz on materials variance involves calculating the total materials variance using a flexed budget approach, given budgeted and actual levels of activity and costs."</data>
      <data key="d2">ae2d4ea94e8ed5a50e75345ffd684969</data>
