      <data key="d1">"The quiz on fixed overhead expenditure involves calculating the actual fixed overhead expenditure given a variance and budgeted overhead."</data>
      <data key="d2">ae2d4ea94e8ed5a50e75345ffd684969</data>
      <data key="d7">20</data>
