      <data key="d6">bbf61f9cd3e14f46a010d704e86be008</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ADVERSE MATERIALS USAGE VARIANCE QUIZ&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz asks which of the following is unlikely to be an explanation for an adverse materials usage variance. The options are stricter quality control, bulk discount, cheaper material being purchased, and change in mix of materials. The correct answer is bulk discount."</data>
