    <node id="&quot;SALES MIX VARIANCE QUIZ&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves calculating the sales mix variance for three products (X, Y, Z) with given budgeted and actual sales data. The correct answer is $200 favorable."</data>
