    <node id="&quot;MATERIALS YIELD VARIANCE QUIZ&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves calculating the materials yield variance for a standard cost of a 10-liter tin of metal paint. The standard cost includes 5 liters of A at $6 per liter, 3 liters of B at $4 per liter, and 2 liters of C at $9 per liter. During the period, 1,020 tins were produced requiring 5,400 liters of A and 3,200 liters of B."</data>
      <data key="d2">01294aa83ab1143451866d43087f9eba</data>
