      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz focuses on identifying the most suitable non-financial performance indicator (NFPI) for monitoring quality, with options including throughput volume, new customers, customer complaints, and transactions per customer."</data>
      <data key="d2">9c3ce103fc83f7ae19dde7d2e5b4ef01</data>
