    <node id="&quot;QUALITY OF KEY PERFORMANCE INDICATORS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz addresses the necessary qualities of key performance indicators (KPIs), focusing on whether they need to be measurable, financially quantifiable, relevant, and specific."</data>
