    <node id="&quot;IMPROVING FINANCIAL POSITION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves evaluating methods to improve Litpan&#8217;s financial position, such as selling old inventory at a discount, obtaining a long-term loan, and extending payment terms with suppliers."</data>
      <data key="d2">9c3ce103fc83f7ae19dde7d2e5b4ef01</data>
