    <node id="&quot;DIVISION A&quot;">
      <data key="d0" />
      <data key="d1">Division A is a part of Bath Co that purchases fittings from Division B and has the potential to buy fittings externally for $65 per set if given autonomy. Additionally, Division A is the adaptor division of Portable Garage Co, producing adaptors used to charge mobile devices and laptops.</data>
      <data key="d2">078e47b3223db97709a37da2a01302c5,34f2c5c9d893c1b631ed1646193eebf4,a5a7a3e9a59209ce811c1f9470684fa6</data>
