    </node>
    <node id="&quot;REVISED ASSETS FORMULA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"FORMULAS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Revised assets = $2,000,000 - $100,000 (Old machinery) + $300,000 (New machinery) - $300,000 (cash paid for new machinery) &#8722; $60,000 (Depreciation charge on new machinery) + $125,000 (Cash on sale of old machinery) = $1,965,000"</data>
      <data key="d2">2922f29fc45ffc98655fc81f9a40fa79</data>
      <data key="d4">1</data>
      <data key="d5">1318</data>
      <data key="d6">0f642f63d4af4fc38298822bfc952719</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;ROI FORMULA&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"FORMULAS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"ROI = ($245,000/$1,965,000) * 100% = 12.5%"</data>
      <data key="d2">2922f29fc45ffc98655fc81f9a40fa79</data>
      <data key="d4">1</data>
      <data key="d5">1319</data>
      <data key="d6">e017ad1f09b049a7ad41d5a11dc1e3d9</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;NON-FINANCIAL PERFORMANCE MEASURES QUIZ&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The quiz asks which of the performance measures used by Wickens Co are non-financial. The measures listed are orders received, staff turnover, quick ratio, and receivables days."</data>
      <data key="d2">2922f29fc45ffc98655fc81f9a40fa79</data>
      <data key="d4">2</data>
      <data key="d5">1320</data>
      <data key="d6">5cbced0ba7044b7490f520a436261c57</data>
    </node>
