    <node id="&quot;DISTRIBUTION COST CALCULATION FOR A CUSTOMER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"FORMULAS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The distribution cost for a customer is calculated by summing the transport cost per order and the processing cost per order, then multiplying by the number of orders."</data>
