    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THROUGHPUT CONTRIBUTION PER UNIT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"FORMULAS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Throughput contribution per unit" is calculated as the selling price per unit minus the direct material cost per unit. This metric is essential for understanding the profitability of a product by determining the contribution of each unit sold after accounting for the cost of raw materials.</data>
      <data key="d2">8c5f3adb7ce0099b89e3e7e2687c2a68,cdba52ee4f0e2669ccb29b10b23e609a</data>
      <data key="d7">12</data>
