    </node>
    <node id="&quot;LIFE CYCLE COSTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Life cycle costs include all costs associated with the life of a product, from planning and concept design to distribution and customer service."</data>
      <data key="d2">cdba52ee4f0e2669ccb29b10b23e609a</data>
