    <node id="&quot;CLOSING TARGET COST GAP QUIZ&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz assesses methods to close a target cost gap for a product, including substituting raw materials with cheaper versions, and understanding the implications of various cost-reduction strategies."</data>
