      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The quiz on lifetime costs involves identifying which costs should be included in the calculation of the lifetime costs of a product. The options include research and development costs, design costs, testing costs, advertising costs, and production costs."</data>
