      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The quiz on target costing description involves identifying the correct definition of target costing from a set of options. The correct answer describes target costing as identifying the market price of a product and then subtracting the desired profit margin to arrive at the target cost."</data>
