      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves identifying the environmental cost classification for testing tea for contaminants. The company grows different types of tea leaves, blends them, and tests them for contaminants in line with food safety legislation. Recently, high levels of contaminated soil were identified in one tea plantation due to a new pesticide."</data>
