      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves categorizing normal and abnormal losses in terms of environmental cost classifications. Normal loss costs are spread over good units of production, potentially becoming hidden costs, while abnormal losses are reported separately as conventional costs."</data>
