    <node id="&quot;SUNK COST&quot;">
      <data key="d0" />
      <data key="d1">"Sunk costs are costs that have already been incurred and cannot be recovered. They are not relevant to future decision-making. For example, the $1.20 per metre for the cable is a sunk cost."</data>
      <data key="d2">77d0f2f7f5d6dc47dd22962bc1f3d777,c83587f345021d1addffee7f64b09dbc</data>
      <data key="d7">18</data>
