    </node>
    <node id="&quot;REVISED TOTAL DIVISIONAL NET LOSS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves calculating the revised total divisional net loss for Lauda Co if Division A is shut down. It includes saving variable costs, divisional fixed costs, and a portion of allocated Head Office costs."</data>
      <data key="d2">42cd34884f35d28c36f2156eefcb5c76</data>
