      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves determining which products (L, M, and S) should be further processed in Division B to optimize profit. It compares incremental revenue from further processing to the variable cost per unit."</data>
      <data key="d2">42cd34884f35d28c36f2156eefcb5c76</data>
      <data key="d4">1</data>
      <data key="d5">1393</data>
