    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BREAK-EVEN NUMBER OF PIZZAS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves calculating the break-even number of pizzas for Mario's pizza business. It considers the variable cost per pizza, the average price charged, and the annual fixed costs."</data>
      <data key="d2">42cd34884f35d28c36f2156eefcb5c76</data>
      <data key="d4">1</data>
      <data key="d5">1394</data>
