      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves calculating the minimum revenue required for production to break even for a company that makes two products. The quiz provides contribution to sales ratios, selling prices, maximum demand, and fixed costs, and asks for the minimum revenue required for production to break even."</data>
