      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves determining which products should be produced to maximize profits given limited direct labour hours. The scenario includes planned production levels, selling prices, raw material costs, direct labour costs, variable overhead costs, fixed overhead costs, and profit per unit for four products. The quiz requires calculating the contribution per labour hour for each product and ranking them to decide the optimal production mix."</data>
