      <data key="d1">"This quiz focuses on understanding the shadow price of material B in a linear programming context where the objective is to maximize profit. The scenario includes the current market price of material B and the shadow price. The quiz tests the understanding of how the shadow price affects the contribution and the maximum price that should be paid for additional material."</data>
