    <node id="&quot;MAINTENANCE COST CALCULATION&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"FORMULAS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The formula for calculating maintenance costs for an order is: Setup cost per setup * Number of setups + Routine maintenance cost per hour * Number of hours. For the given order, the calculation is $58.33 per setup * 3 setups + $14.98 per hour * 56 hours = $1,014."</data>
      <data key="d2">e2466c934645bbb746c51b6c2bee67aa</data>
      <data key="d4">1</data>
      <data key="d5">1453</data>
