      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"This quiz involves adjusting Igloo Co's sales performance based on actual inflation and market size. The budgeted sales were $30.9m within a market worth $61.8m, with an assumed inflation of 3%. The actual inflation was 2%, and the market was worth $65m. The adjusted sales revenue figure is calculated to be $32.5m."</data>
