    <node id="&quot;PRODUCTION MANAGER'S BONUS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"A food production company has recently employed a new production manager. The production manager&#8217;s remuneration includes a bonus that is linked to the monthly cost variances including the materials price, yield, and mix variances. The quiz asks which statements about linking the production manager&#8217;s bonus to these variances are true."</data>
      <data key="d2">27fde199847b14399dfca384e07a77a4</data>
