    <node id="&quot;ECONOMY&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"ECONOMY" is a component of Value for Money (VFM) that focuses on the amount of resources used in operations, primarily concerned with inputs and costs. It considers whether resources are acquired at the required quality for the lowest price.</data>
      <data key="d2">3d86fa6cff193e8919165e686b8e6427,963bb5be84f30224d6e25ea423602dfd</data>
      <data key="d4">2</data>
