    </node>
    <node id="&quot;EFFECTIVENESS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"EFFECTIVENESS" is a component of Value for Money (VFM) that assesses the achievement of intended results and policy objectives. It focuses on outputs regardless of inputs, measuring whether overall objectives have been met.</data>
      <data key="d2">3d86fa6cff193e8919165e686b8e6427,963bb5be84f30224d6e25ea423602dfd</data>
      <data key="d4">4</data>
