    <node id="&quot;IMPLEMENTATION AND EVALUATION OF EPOS AND ERPS IN XYZ STORES&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CASES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"IMPLEMENTATION AND EVALUATION OF EPOS AND ERPS IN XYZ STORES"

XYZ Stores operates a chain of 10 convenience stores with basic information systems. The case involves the implementation and evaluation of Electronic Point of Sale (EPOS) and Enterprise Resource Planning Systems (ERPS) to improve operational efficiency.</data>
      <data key="d2">2ad6c0ee81f4b0da1c6b2f2821dff6b6,9674b500a570fa3a7bf9957943ff48a7</data>
