    </node>
    <node id="&quot;QUIZ ON ACTIVITY-BASED COSTING AT BBB&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"QUIZZES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The quiz involves questions about the sales price for a typical GC using the current method of absorbing overheads, the cost of a GC using activity-based costing, the cost per unit of a typical EX using activity-based costing, and statements about the usefulness of activity-based costing and environmental activity-based costing."</data>
