      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"It can only be used to solve programmes with two variables (e.g. two products)."</data>
      <data key="d2">3ff25cf1ebad4d5b8f8a7bbfefd288ab</data>
      <data key="d4">0</data>
