      <data key="d0">"CASES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Cara Co produces two products, Seebach and Herdorf, requiring specific amounts of materials, labor, and machine hours. The company faces constraints in resources and has to meet minimum production requirements for Herdorf in the first two months. The case involves using linear programming to optimize production and resource allocation over three months."</data>
