    <node id="&quot;LINEAR PROGRAMMING GRAPH INTERPRETATION FOR MONTH 3&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EXAMPLES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The interpretation of the linear programming graph for month 3 indicates that labour will be a slack variable if no other resources change, even if demand for either product increases."</data>
