    <node id="&quot;RESOURCE OPTIMIZATION AND CONTRIBUTION ANALYSIS FOR HOME ELECTRICS CO&#8217;S DIVISIONS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CASES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Home Electrics Co manufactures electrical appliances for domestic use and is made up of two divisions. The Small Appliances division produces products like the Blender (Product B) and the Toaster (Product T). The standard cost cards per unit for each product include selling price, direct materials, direct labour, and variable overheads."</data>
