      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Blender (Product B) is one of the products manufactured by the Small Appliances division of Home Electrics Co. It has a selling price of $80, direct materials cost of $10, direct labour cost of $21, and variable overheads of $12."</data>
