      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Toaster (Product T) is one of the products manufactured by the Small Appliances division of Home Electrics Co. It has a selling price of $120, direct materials cost of $15, direct labour cost of $35, and variable overheads of $18."</data>
