    <node id="&quot;PRODUCTION CONSTRAINTS FOR PRODUCT B AND T&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"FORMULAS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The production constraints for Product B and T are given by the formulas: Materials: 2B + 3T = 2000, Labour: 3B + 5T = 3200."</data>
      <data key="d2">88e696361bcc111f3d87032d375208f9</data>
