      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Supervisor's time allocation for hormone process refers to the distribution of the supervisor's time and effort across the hormone-adding process for the male and female versions of the perfume."</data>
      <data key="d2">853a1c1f12ff5eee7a78129a3fed226f</data>
      <data key="d4">0</data>
      <data key="d5">2119</data>
      <data key="d6">88f3b0d8d26146b5ab4e654b17c55dbd</data>
