      <data key="d0">"CONCEPTS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Cost reduction strategies for hormone process refer to the methods and actions taken to decrease expenses and improve profitability, such as negotiating lower material costs or optimizing production processes."</data>
      <data key="d2">853a1c1f12ff5eee7a78129a3fed226f</data>
