      <data key="d0">"CASES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Hair Co manufactures three types of electrical goods for hair: curlers (C), straightening irons (S), and dryers (D). The budgeted sales prices and volumes for the next year are provided, along with the standard cost card for each product. The case involves calculating the weighted average contribution to sales ratio, total break-even revenue, and drawing a multi-product profit-volume chart."</data>
      <data key="d2">a5995fbeaf1e8bc061f219d79f9689d1</data>
