      <data key="d0">"EXAMPLES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Hair Co manufactures three types of electrical goods for hair: curlers (C), straightening irons (S), and dryers (D). The budgeted sales prices and volumes for the next year are provided, along with the standard cost card for each product."</data>
      <data key="d2">a5995fbeaf1e8bc061f219d79f9689d1</data>
