    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MULTI-PRODUCT PV CHART&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EXAMPLES"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The multi-product PV chart compares profit against sales revenue for products C, S, and D. It includes a solid line for 'Most profitable first' and a dashed line for 'Constant mix'."</data>
      <data key="d2">feda6b4c9964e8465efd20e4a6167582</data>
