    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BREAK-EVEN POINT FOR HIGHEST RANKING FIRST&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"FORMULAS"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Break-even point for highest ranking first is calculated by dividing fixed costs of $640,000 by Product C's C/S ratio of 0.55, resulting in $1,163,636."</data>
      <data key="d2">feda6b4c9964e8465efd20e4a6167582</data>
      <data key="d4">1</data>
