      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;USE OF INFORMATION IN CONTROL&quot;" target="&quot;INFORMATION SYSTEMS&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Different types of Information Systems support the various levels of management control: EIS for strategic, DSS and MIS for tactical, and TPS for operational."</data>
      <data key="d11">d4fd6778c3735e1144e70c31e7a057e5</data>
      <data key="d12">bb9b1d736df94c1cb21aa426e3bc48c7</data>
      <data key="d13">23</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
