    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;KNOWLEDGE&quot;" target="&quot;WISDOM&quot;">
      <data key="d9">5.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Knowledge" and "Wisdom" are closely related concepts. Knowledge is the understanding of data relationships and is applied to make sound judgments and decisions. When knowledge is effectively utilized, it leads to improved decision-making, which is referred to as wisdom. In essence, knowledge is the foundation that, when applied correctly, transforms into wisdom.</data>
      <data key="d11">0300615aebb7ef4e2e5e1ed830623ea3,75aa284e3bf8d3b64f3e1feff1c7b3fb,9cc1a2ea3eea29b6f534abb18ab94b2d</data>
