    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;TARGET COSTING&quot;" target="&quot;TARGET COST GAP&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Target cost gap is the difference between the current cost and the target cost in target costing."</data>
      <data key="d11">b6aae482ada9c34bf0afb23a1a9ef1fa</data>
      <data key="d12">42f41f1146d541aa895e27f393a12181</data>
      <data key="d13">185</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;TARGET COSTING&quot;" target="&quot;APPLICATION TO SERVICE INDUSTRIES&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The concept of Target Costing is discussed in the context of its application to service industries, highlighting the challenges and considerations."</data>
      <data key="d11">9d54588af94d453794e574c052472b3e</data>
      <data key="d12">684ad0aeb8cd4c918be5205e026dab3f</data>
      <data key="d13">186</data>
