    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;TARGET COSTING&quot;" target="&quot;EXAMPLE OF TARGET COSTING FOR SERVICES&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The concept of Target Costing is illustrated through the Example of Target Costing for Services, where Gates &amp; Jobs Co applies target costing to match a competitor's price for tax returns."</data>
      <data key="d11">9d54588af94d453794e574c052472b3e</data>
      <data key="d12">42b26eca2bda41c3bdea4497af2bcbe7</data>
