    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;TARGET COSTING&quot;" target="&quot;NARROWING THE TARGET COST GAP&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The concept of Target Costing includes methods for Narrowing the Target Cost Gap, involving multi-disciplinary teams and various cost-reduction strategies."</data>
      <data key="d11">9d54588af94d453794e574c052472b3e</data>
