    <edge source="&quot;TARGET COSTING&quot;" target="&quot;INVESTMENT REQUIRED&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The concept of Target Costing involves determining the Investment Required to produce a product."</data>
