    <edge source="&quot;TARGET COSTING&quot;" target="&quot;RETURN ON INVESTMENT (ROI)&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The concept of Target Costing involves determining the needed Return on Investment (ROI) to calculate the target profit."</data>
      <data key="d11">9d54588af94d453794e574c052472b3e</data>
