    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;FIXED COSTS&quot;" target="&quot;DEPRECIATION&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Both Fixed costs and Depreciation are irrelevant to decision-making as they do not change with the level of production or sales."</data>
