    <edge source="&quot;SUNK COSTS&quot;" target="&quot;COMMITTED COSTS&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Both Sunk costs and Committed costs are irrelevant to decision-making as they are not incremental costs."</data>
