    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;OPPORTUNITY COST&quot;" target="&quot;RELEVANT COSTING&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Opportunity cost is a key concept in the methodology of relevant costing, as it helps in identifying the costs that will be affected by a specific decision."</data>
      <data key="d11">e0431b989a9611549dff83d93fe89d4b</data>
      <data key="d12">1425c78417504296b08259d9a7eebe28</data>
      <data key="d13">363</data>
