    <edge source="&quot;ASSUMPTION OF CVP ANALYSIS&quot;" target="&quot;WEIGHTED AVERAGE C/S RATIO&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The assumption of a constant pre-determined sales mix in CVP analysis is necessary for calculating the Weighted Average C/S Ratio."</data>
