    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;MAXIMUM CONTRIBUTION CALCULATION&quot;" target="&quot;CONTRIBUTION PER LIMITING FACTOR&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Contribution per limiting factor is used in the maximum contribution calculation to prioritize products."</data>
      <data key="d11">ac68069ef08bb5822225377a605ac206</data>
      <data key="d12">e1553a3871cf4151b9ff13a2de61d820</data>
      <data key="d13">535</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;KEY FACTOR ANALYSIS&quot;" target="&quot;LIMITATIONS OF KEY FACTOR ANALYSIS&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Key Factor Analysis has several limitations, including assumptions of a single objective of profit maximization, constant variable and fixed costs, dealing with only one scarce resource, and applicability only to short-term capacity constraints."</data>
      <data key="d11">ac68069ef08bb5822225377a605ac206</data>
      <data key="d12">35cad8cc8bd44c9bb6042961a612cdf4</data>
      <data key="d13">536</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;KEY FACTOR ANALYSIS&quot;" target="&quot;SHADOW PRICE&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Shadow Price is related to Key Factor Analysis as it represents the additional contribution generated if one more unit of a scarce resource becomes available."</data>
      <data key="d11">ac68069ef08bb5822225377a605ac206</data>
      <data key="d12">a4ca9e509566419ba64e6ef4e8ab4f4c</data>
      <data key="d13">537</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;KEY FACTOR ANALYSIS&quot;" target="&quot;DECISIONS WITH A LIMITING FACTOR&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Decisions with a Limiting Factor are related to Key Factor Analysis as they involve prioritizing products based on the savings per unit of scarce resource."</data>
      <data key="d11">ac68069ef08bb5822225377a605ac206</data>
      <data key="d12">43c94b2fdc774281b00164176faac337</data>
      <data key="d13">538</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;SHADOW PRICE&quot;" target="&quot;GRAPHICAL LINEAR PROGRAMMING&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
