    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;SHADOW PRICE&quot;" target="&quot;SPECIALIST TIMBER&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The shadow price is calculated for the specialist timber to determine the maximum price that should be paid for additional supplies."</data>
