    <edge source="&quot;DECISIONS WITH A LIMITING FACTOR&quot;" target="&quot;MAKE OR BUY QUIZ&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The Make or Buy Quiz is an example of Decisions with a Limiting Factor, determining which components to make in-house and which to buy externally based on the savings per unit of scarce resource."</data>
