    <edge source="&quot;FUNCTIONAL BUDGETS&quot;" target="&quot;BOTTOM-UP BUDGETING&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Bottom-up budgeting involves managers preparing their own functional budgets, which are then reviewed by senior management."</data>
      <data key="d11">bba1095f6b9a360e21d80bc3dc45ff30</data>
      <data key="d12">caa818e2b074416dbb4b676fca0df94d</data>
