    <edge source="&quot;ZERO-BASED BUDGETING (ZBB)&quot;" target="&quot;BUDGETARY CONTROL SYSTEM&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Zero-based budgeting (ZBB) is a method used within a budgetary control system that starts 'from scratch' and requires all costs and benefits to be justified."</data>
