      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The features of ZBB contribute to its benefits such as re-evaluating activities and linking resource allocation to results."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">e994c254c7234a11ae28e2f1a731007e</data>
