    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;FEATURES OF ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;DRAWBACKS OF ZBB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The features of ZBB also lead to some drawbacks such as the need for training and unmanageable paperwork."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">b71a6726392442899a893f6ac439aa0a</data>
