      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;BENEFITS OF ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;DRAWBACKS OF ZBB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The benefits of ZBB are countered by its drawbacks."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">057d760e05424887a15acccedb3f36bd</data>
      <data key="d13">710</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;BENEFITS OF ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;WHEN ZBB IS APPROPRIATE&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The benefits of ZBB make it appropriate for organizations with high discretionary costs."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">2962f20aebad45e7b270830aa91b7289</data>
      <data key="d13">711</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;BENEFITS OF ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;USE OF ZBB IN THE PUBLIC SECTOR&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The benefits of ZBB make it more prevalent in public sector bodies."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">3e32487807314cea889120c2e8c3142b</data>
      <data key="d13">712</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;DRAWBACKS OF ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;ZBB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"ZBB has several drawbacks such as the need for training, unmanageable paperwork, and difficulty in ranking packages."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">bd85b0d0e18e40cfa20214284fbe255d</data>
      <data key="d13">713</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;DRAWBACKS OF ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;WHEN ZBB IS APPROPRIATE&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The drawbacks of ZBB must be considered when determining its appropriateness."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">01a0ce258ced42ccbf16a8bff0462d9b</data>
      <data key="d13">714</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;DRAWBACKS OF ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;USE OF ZBB IN THE PUBLIC SECTOR&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The drawbacks of ZBB must be managed in public sector bodies."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">420c3b750d6a4f31aec0876b8a6c9922</data>
      <data key="d13">715</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WHEN ZBB IS APPROPRIATE&quot;" target="&quot;ZBB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"ZBB is most appropriate in organizations with a high portion of discretionary costs."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">e2e20b798a7e4e9ba0ed11f52f55584f</data>
      <data key="d13">716</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;WHEN ZBB IS APPROPRIATE&quot;" target="&quot;USE OF ZBB IN THE PUBLIC SECTOR&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"ZBB is appropriate in public sector bodies due to its transparency and usefulness in ranking decision packages."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">837f2de009fd4e83acd1ece44f52933f</data>
      <data key="d13">717</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;USE OF ZBB IN THE PUBLIC SECTOR&quot;" target="&quot;ZBB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"ZBB is more prevalent in public sector bodies due to its transparency and usefulness in ranking decision packages."</data>
      <data key="d11">8cdfffc4f5f91dc3af2a0e1a32d28ab4</data>
      <data key="d12">1f09114c97504b018e858edfc01f4ff3</data>
      <data key="d13">718</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;DECISION PACKAGE 2&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Decision package 2 is evaluated under the Zero-Based Budgeting (ZBB) approach, which focuses on justifying all expenses and evaluating decision packages by value for money."</data>
      <data key="d11">ed1f837be30c9135b0fe794ec0162540</data>
      <data key="d12">63d57d2512d24aa8a1f1875fbed10085</data>
      <data key="d13">719</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;ADVANTAGES OF ZBB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"ZBB has several advantages, including a focus on community objectives, evaluation of decision packages by value for money, and identification of operational efficiencies."</data>
      <data key="d11">ed1f837be30c9135b0fe794ec0162540</data>
      <data key="d12">ecc2d1f5440d4359856475c9508f0d53</data>
      <data key="d13">720</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;ZBB&quot;" target="&quot;DISADVANTAGES OF ZBB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"ZBB has several disadvantages, including being time-consuming, potential distraction from other responsibilities, and a focus on short-term objectives over long-term benefits."</data>
      <data key="d11">ed1f837be30c9135b0fe794ec0162540</data>
      <data key="d12">c73cefd09e1740d092dc3d5f9c35fe58</data>
      <data key="d13">721</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;ADVANTAGES OF ABB&quot;" target="&quot;DISADVANTAGES OF ABB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Advantages and disadvantages of ABB provide a comprehensive view of the method's strengths and weaknesses."</data>
      <data key="d11">43b0942a38155115a834866ac07fe119</data>
      <data key="d12">cd6a647845c74907bf37dde15558af22</data>
      <data key="d13">722</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;ADVANTAGES OF ABB&quot;" target="&quot;APPROPRIATENESS OF ABB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The appropriateness of ABB is related to its advantages in managing high overheads and diverse activities."</data>
      <data key="d11">43b0942a38155115a834866ac07fe119</data>
      <data key="d12">8a83b5e47bb24eca8d100f06332b3ecb</data>
      <data key="d13">723</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;DISADVANTAGES OF ABB&quot;" target="&quot;APPROPRIATENESS OF ABB&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"The appropriateness of ABB is also influenced by its disadvantages, such as complexity and expense."</data>
      <data key="d11">43b0942a38155115a834866ac07fe119</data>
      <data key="d12">4540839425054d7b803d234cb44e4677</data>
      <data key="d13">724</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;FEEDBACK CONTROL&quot;" target="&quot;CLOSED-LOOP SYSTEM&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Feedback control is a type of closed-loop system.""A closed-loop system relies on feedback control to monitor and adjust outputs."</data>
      <data key="d11">43b0942a38155115a834866ac07fe119</data>
      <data key="d12">ca79fcb5704346d2b1738af8e1475008</data>
      <data key="d13">725</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;FEEDBACK CONTROL&quot;" target="&quot;OPEN-LOOP SYSTEM&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Open-loop systems lack the feedback control present in closed-loop systems."</data>
      <data key="d11">43b0942a38155115a834866ac07fe119</data>
      <data key="d12">33662ef5986a40c48e64c84f31e20f75</data>
      <data key="d13">726</data>
      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
