      <data key="d14">0</data>
    </edge>
    <edge source="&quot;FORECASTING&quot;" target="&quot;FLEXIBLE BUDGETS&quot;">
      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Forecasting is related to Flexible Budgets as it involves making assumptions about the external environment, which can be addressed using flexible budgets.")</data>
