    <edge source="&quot;MARKET SKIMMING PRICING&quot;" target="&quot;ANTI-MALARIA DRUG&quot;">
      <data key="d9">2.0</data>
      <data key="d10">Market skimming pricing is an alternative strategy considered for the launch of the anti-malaria drug. This approach aims to maximize profits from early adopters by taking advantage of the drug's unique nature and high development costs. By implementing market skimming pricing, the goal is to generate high initial cash flows, thereby capitalizing on the drug's initial market entry.</data>
