      <data key="d9">1.0</data>
      <data key="d10">"Both methods (RI and ROI) will favour Division A because performance for Division A will be assessed on a lower value for assets due to higher accumulated depreciation."</data>
      <data key="d11">a5a7a3e9a59209ce811c1f9470684fa6</data>
